01:23:03,370 --> 01:23:04,930
you just figured something out.

820
01:23:39,470 --> 01:23:41,130
Remember what you asked me?

821
01:23:46,070 --> 01:23:46,870
What did I ask you?

822
01:23:51,670 --> 01:23:53,430
Do I believe in karma?

823
01:24:01,700 --> 01:24:03,700
I replied that I believe in the idea of karma.

824
01:24:05,200 --> 01:24:07,000
If we were meant to share karma together,

825
01:24:08,030 --> 01:24:09,470
we will meet again.

826
01:24:12,770 --> 01:24:14,170
Just like the two of us now

827
01:24:18,230 --> 01:24:19,730
But I do believe the karma is real.

828
01:24:31,100 --> 01:24:31,900
Wait a minute.

829
01:24:40,630 --> 01:24:41,430
You are…

830
01:25:46,230 --> 01:25:47,970
The official press event for The Memory the series.

831
01:25:48,130 --> 01:25:49,570
Why don’t we know any of this?

832
01:25:50,530 --> 01:25:52,170
Why don’t you just leave the Deam Company?

833
01:25:52,370 --> 01:25:54,330
For the safety of those around you.

834
01:25:55,670 --> 01:25:56,730
If you’re going to hold a grudge,

835
01:25:57,070 --> 01:25:58,300
blame yourself instead.

836
01:25:58,770 --> 01:26:00,870
You will put people around you in trouble too.

837
01:26:02,570 --> 01:26:03,370
What are you going to do?

838
01:26:04,630 --> 01:26:05,430
I’m here now,

839
01:26:07,070 --> 01:26:08,570
you guys can let him go.

